    		                		<h1>Watchdog slams care at hospital for vulnerable adults</h1>
            		<p class="details">
                                                                                                                        <a href="mailto:richard.young@thecomet.net " class="email">Richard Young </a>
                                                                                                                                Tuesday, January 17, 2012 <br/> 3:27 PM

                    					<div class="share-actions">
	<iframe src="http://www.facebook.com/plugins/like.php?href=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thecomet.net%3A80%2Fnews%2Fwatchdog_slams_care_at_hospital_for_vulnerable_adults_1_1179824&amp;layout=button_count&amp;show_faces=false&amp;width=120&amp;action=recommend&amp;font=arial&amp;colorscheme=light&amp;height=21" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" style="border:none; overflow:hidden; width:120px; height:21px;" allowTransparency="true"></iframe>
	<iframe role="presentation" src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets/tweet_button.html?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thecomet.net%3A80%2Fnews%2Fwatchdog_slams_care_at_hospital_for_vulnerable_adults_1_1179824&count=horizontal&text=Watchdog slams care at hospital for vulnerable adults" frameBorder="0" scrolling="no" style="width: 100px; height: 21px;" allowTransparency="allowtransparency"/></iframe>
</div>            		</p>
    		                	   </div>
    		        			
            	<p class="lead"><!--PSTYLE=SF Web Summary--><p>A health service watchdog has heavily criticised a hospital after inspectors found allegations of abuse were not being properly responded to, while staff were disrespectful to patients and had no clear understanding of restraint. </p></p>
            
				<a name="sharinganchor"></a>
<div class="in-page-actions">
	<ul class="user-actions">
				  <li class="your-view"><a href="#article-comments">Comments</a></li>
